FBIS3-39871 "drweu036_q_94016" FBIS-WEU-94-036 Document Type:Daily Report 23 Feb 1994 TURKEY PKK Attack Spills Nearly 700 Barrels in Batman NC2202220794 London Kanal-6 Television in Turkish 1700 GMT 22 Feb 94 NC2202220794 London Kanal-6 Television Language: Turkish Article Type:BFN [Text] The BOTAS [Pipeline and Petroleum Transport Corporation] oil terminal in Batman came under PKK [Workers Party of Kurdistan] rocket attack yesterday. The attack took place at 1910 last night. Three petrol tanks were hit in the attack, which was launched from the Mardin-Batman highway. Nearly 700 barrels of crude oil leaked from the tanks into the surrounding area but did not catch fire.
